record.title: PRINTING OF PROCEEDINGS HAD DURING RECESS
record.narrative:
PRINTING OF PROCEEDINGS HAD DURING RECESS -- (House of Representatives - November 07, 2007)

[Page: H13213]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent that the proceedings had during the recess be printed in the Record.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from North Carolina?
